n with Rydberg electromagnetically induced transparency, enables\nstudies of photonic fractional quantum Hall fluids[16,17] and direct detection\nof anyons[18-19].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 19:47:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2017 00:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
