-Lidov\nevolution, while retrograde binaries frequently flip their inclination and\n$\\sim50\\%$ of them are destroyed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 21:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Feb 2016 18:17:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-06"}
