 coherent with that expected for the\nregion. Further analysis on a larger sample of galaxies will follow in order to\nunderstand how unique this decomposition is or how it evolves from one\nenvironment to another.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 21:05:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 09:10:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
