\ninfinite-dimensional Lie algebra containing three families: two of them span\nthe semidirect sum of the Witt algebra and scalar supertranslations and the\nthird generates vector supertranslations. We manage to comprehend that the\ninfinite connected group is the precise diffeomorphisms subgroup allowing to\nlocally deform the AdS background into AdS waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 21:10:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 03:53:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 6 Dec 2015 21:25:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2016 05:50:02 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 21:59:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-27"}
