al Big Bang singularity after quantization gets\nreplaced by the full-fledged quantum degeneracy. At the\nquantum-phase-transition singularity, operator $Q(\\tau_{(EP)})$ becomes\nunobservable and acquires a non-diagonalizable Jordan-block structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 08:40:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-05"}
