{~yr}$) formation of planetesimals. If erosive\ncollisions prevent this, SI might be triggered for specific disk conditions.\nThe numerical approach introduced in this work is ideally suited for studying\nplanetesimal formation and pebble delivery simultaneously and will help build a\ncoherent picture of the start of the planet formation process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 15:38:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
